<L>__{interior john's bedroom night}
<A>__{luke lies in the crook of his father's arm, his own arms full of penguins, turtles, a black dog and an opossum. john reads him a letter, the yellow envelope open on the bed.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{and give a big hug to pengui, little pengui, big turtley, little turtley, kiki and opossumy. lots and lots of love, mommy.}
